---
const footerMobileTitleLines = ["Be a Good", "Coiner"];
---

<footer
  id="contact"
  class="relative overflow-hidden bg-[var(--bg-product-surface)] px-6 pb-8 pt-[95px] text-[var(--text-inverse)] md:px-8 md:pb-14 md:pt-[155px]"
>
  <img
    src="/figma/footer/bg.svg"
    alt=""
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="pointer-events-none absolute left-0 top-0 w-full max-w-none select-none"
    loading="lazy"
  />

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto flex max-w-[1094px] flex-col gap-12 md:gap-24">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-12 text-center">
      <div class="flex w-full max-w-[934px] flex-col items-center gap-6 md:gap-8">
        <div class="flex w-full flex-col items-center gap-4">
          <p
            class="font-['Noto_Sans_JP'] text-[18px] font-bold leading-[27px] tracking-[0.08em] text-[var(--text-inverse)] md:text-[26px] md:leading-[39px] md:tracking-[1.04px]"
          >
            トレードを、感覚から仕組みへ。
          </p>
          <h2
            class="font-avenir hidden text-[clamp(68px,7.5vw,107px)] font-black leading-[107px] text-[var(--text-inverse)] md:block md:whitespace-nowrap"
          >
            Be a Good Coiner
          </h2>
          <h2
            class="font-avenir text-[68px] font-black leading-[68px] tracking-[-0.05em] text-[var(--text-inverse)] md:hidden"
            aria-label="Be a Good Coiner"
          >
            {footerMobileTitleLines.map((line, index) => (
              <>
                {line}
                {index < footerMobileTitleLines.length - 1 && <br />}
              </>
            ))}
          </h2>
        </div>

        <p
          class="hidden w-full text-center font-['Noto_Sans_JP'] text-[16px] font-medium leading-8 tracking-[0.64px] text-[var(--text-inverse)] md:block"
        >
          グッドコイナーは、感覚や感情に左右されず、<br />
          明確なルールと目的に基づいて暗号資産を売買するトレード管理アプリです。<br />
          「Be a Good Coiner」を合言葉に、再現性のあるトレードを優しくサポートします。
        </p>
        <p
          class="w-full text-center font-inter-jp text-[14px] font-normal leading-[1.9] tracking-[0.04em] text-[var(--text-inverse)] md:hidden"
        >
          グッドコイナーは、感覚や感情に左右されず、<br />
          明確なルールと目的に基づいて暗号資産を売買するトレード管理アプリです。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex w-full max-w-80 flex-col items-center gap-4 md:gap-5">
        <a
          id="download"
          href="#"
          class="inline-flex h-14 w-full items-center justify-center gap-2.5 rounded-[82px] bg-[var(--accent-yellow)] px-8 py-3 md:h-auto md:py-4"
        >
          <img
            src="/assets/icons/Finder_Icon_macOS.png"
            alt=""
            aria-hidden="true"
            class="h-7 w-7"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <span
            class="font-['Noto_Sans_JP'] text-[16px] font-bold leading-4 text-[var(--text-primary)] md:text-[18px] md:leading-[32.38px] md:tracking-[0.18px]"
          >
            Mac版をダウンロード
          </span>
        </a>

        <p
          class="w-full text-center font-['Noto_Sans_JP'] text-[12px] font-normal leading-[15.6px] tracking-[0.48px] text-[var(--text-tertiary)] md:whitespace-nowrap md:leading-3"
        >
          ※現在GMOコインユーザーのみ利用可能。<br class="md:hidden" />
          順次拡張予定です。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.12)] pt-12 md:border-0 md:pt-0">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center">
        <img
          src="/assets/logo/header_logo.svg"
          alt="グッドコイナー"
          class="h-auto w-[227px] brightness-0 invert md:w-[196px]"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        </a>

        <div class="flex w-full flex-col items-center gap-6 md:max-w-[568px] md:items-end md:gap-3">
          <div class="flex w-full max-w-80 flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-6 gap-y-2 md:max-w-none md:flex-nowrap md:justify-end md:gap-y-0">
          <a
            href="#contact"
            class="font-inter-jp text-[11px] font-bold leading-[32.38px] tracking-[0.08em] text-[var(--text-inverse)] md:text-[13px] md:tracking-[1.04px]"
          >
            お問い合わせ
          </a>
          <a
            href="#howto"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-0.5 font-['Noto_Sans_JP'] text-[11px] font-bold leading-[32.38px] tracking-[0.04em] text-[var(--text-inverse)] md:text-[13px] md:tracking-[0.52px]"
          >
            利用方法
            <img
              src="/assets/icons/arrow_outward.svg"
              alt=""
              aria-hidden="true"
              class="h-6 w-6 brightness-0 invert"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </a>
          <a
            href="#"
            class="font-inter-jp text-[11px] font-bold leading-[32.38px] tracking-[0.08em] text-[var(--text-inverse)] md:text-[13px] md:tracking-[1.04px]"
          >
            プライバシーポリシー
          </a>
          <a
            href="#"
            class="font-inter-jp text-[11px] font-bold leading-[32.38px] tracking-[0.08em] text-[var(--text-inverse)] md:whitespace-nowrap md:text-[13px] md:tracking-[1.04px]"
          >
            特定商取引法に基づく表記
          </a>
        </div>

          <p class="font-avenir w-full text-center text-[12px] font-normal leading-3 tracking-[1.56px] text-[var(--text-secondary)] md:text-right">
            © 2026 Good Coiner. All rights reserved.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
